The data table includes general information on the location of the borehole, well construction information, location uncertainty and remarks. Information sources are included in the dataset. The HeaderURI for a particular borehole is the cross-referencing link (foreign key) used to associate the borehole with web based information on the well construction, pictures or other information, specific to one feature. The data is displayed using a circle with a transparent center. Layer files containing the symbology for these data layers can be found in the USGIN repository at http://repository.usgin.org/uri_gin/usgin/dlio/532.]]></Abstract>
